        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "**The opening leaf, as a whole object.** Quire structure, the ruling of the page, and the erased ownership inscription in the top margin all belong to *folio 1r entire* — not to any single drawn region. This note is attached to the whole object (no box), so the Viewer frames the folio rather than pinning a spot on it.",
          "purpose": "commenting"
